 Bohra]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| Rocky Pratap Singh || A naag from Takshak clan, Shivangi's husband, Mahendra Pratap Singh and Vasudha's son, Yamini's adoptive son. || style=\"text-align:center;\" | Alive || {{N/A|}} || {{CMain|Main}} || {{cGuest|Guest}} || {{N/A|}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[Kinshuk Mahajan]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| Rudra || A naag from Sheshnag clan, friend of Shivangi. || style=\"text-align:center;\" | Dead || {{N/A|}} || {{CMain|Main}} || colspan=2 {{N/A|}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[Karishma Tanna]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| Ruhi || A naagin from Sheshnag clan, later reincarnated as Bela || style=\"text-align:center;\" | Dead || colspan=2 {{N/A|}} || {{cGuest|Guest}} || {{N/A|}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[Surbhi Jyoti]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| Bela Mahir Sehgal || A naagin, Naagrani of Sheshnag clan, the reincarnation of Ruhi, Juhi's elder sister, Mahir's wife. || style=\"text-align:center;\" | Dead || colspan=2 {{N/A|}} || {{cMain|Main}} || {{N/A|}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| Shravani Mihir Sippi || A naagin, Naagrani of Sheshnag clan, the reincarnation of Bela, Mihir's wife. || style=\"text-align:center;\" | Dead || colspan=2 {{N/A|}} || {{cMain|Main}} || {{N/A|}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[Pearl V Puri]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| Mahir Sehgal || Andy and Sumitra's son, Sumitra (naagin)'s adoptive son; Kuhu's elder brother; Yuvraj, Aditya and Pratham's half-brother; Ruhi/Bela's husband. || style=\"text-align:center;\" | Dead || colspan=2 {{N/A|}} || {{CMain|Main}} || {{N/A|}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| Mihir Sippi || The reincarnation of Mahir, Samarjeet and Kanika's son, Mohit's younger brother, Shravani's husband. || style=\"text-align:center;\"| Dead || colspan=2 {{N/A|}} || {{CMain|Main}} || {{N/A|}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[Rakshanda Khan]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| Sumitra || A naa